name: endBad1
Narrator: Stop, Stop, Stop. Basta. Qua ci tirano pomodori. Rifacciamo.
NarratorTranslation: Stop, stop, stop! Enough… Too many tomatoes. Let's start over
NarratorTranslationEs: ¡Alto, alto, alto! ¡Basta! Demasiados tomates. Empecemos de nuevo.

name: endBad2
Narrator: Stop. Stop. Allora la scena non sta piacendo, non va bene, dobbiamo interrom—
NarratorTranslation: Stop. Stop. The scene is not to their liking, this is not good… We have to interr—
NarratorTranslationEs: Alto. Alto. La escena no les gusta, esto no es bueno... Tenemos que interr...

name: endBad3
Narrator: Stop, stop, stop, stop. Non va bene, la scena va tagliata. Ricominciamo.
NarratorTranslation: Stop, stop, stop, stop… This is not good, scene needs to be cut… Let's start over
NarratorTranslationEs: Alto, alto, alto, alto... Esto no es bueno, la escena necesita ser cortada... Empecemos de nuevo.

name: endGood2
Narrator: Bene maschere, brave, brave, bene cosí

name: endQuestion1
Narrator: E voi, cosa ne pensate? Erano credibili? Erano capaci?
NarratorTranslation: And you. What did you think? Was it credible? Were they capable?
NarratorTranslationEs: Y a ti. ¿Qué te pareció? ¿Fue creíble? ¿Fueron buenos?

name: endQuestion2
Narrator: E voi, pubblico, cosa ne pensate di quello che hanno detto i modelli?
NarratorTranslation: And you. What did YOU think of what the models said?
NarratorTranslationEs: Y a ti. ¿Qué te pareció lo que dijeron los modelos?

name: endQuestion3
Narrator: E voi, pubblico, cosa ne pensate dei modelli? Erano credibili?
NarratorTranslation: And you, what did YOU think about the models? Were they credible?
NarratorTranslationEs: Y a ti, ¿qué te parecieron los modelos? ¿Fueron creíbles?

name: endQuestion4
Narrator: E voi, pubblico, cosa ne pensate dei modelli? Li capite? Ci credete?
NarratorTranslation: And you - what do you think about the models? Did you understand them? Did you believe them?
NarratorTranslationEs: Y tú, ¿qué opinas de los modelos? ¿Los entendiste? ¿Te los creíste?

name: endQuestion5
Narrator: E voi, pubblico, cosa ne pensate dei modelli? Li capite? Gli credete?
NarratorTranslation: And you - what do you think about the models? Did you understand… Did you believe it?
NarratorTranslationEs: Y tú ¿qué opinas de los modelos? ¿Lo entendiste...? ¿Te lo creíste?
